rComments: Amazing instructor, full of passion, which makes going to class fun even if you don't agree with his opinions.  Not an easy class, but I learned so much from it, and him.
A tough class, but one of the best teachers ever. He is one of those people you remember for the rest of your life,and he doesn't mind throwing in a life lesson or twelve every now and then.
Great teacher.  Tells you what you need to know, quirky personality keeps class interesting.
Not easy, but an awesome teacher
One of the best teachers I have ever had
